{"prompt": "Generate a website for a restaurant chain. The website should be elegant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elegant Eats</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #8B0000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #A0522D; /* Sienna - a subtle, warm contrast */\n            --text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --background-color: #F5F5DC; /* Beige */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', cursive;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #eee;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.7)),